# Installation of GHC 8.0.0

## Installation Script

~~~
# get distribution  
cd $HOME/Downloads  

-- wget https://www.haskell.org/ghc/dist/7.10.3/ghc-7.10.3-x86_64-deb8-linux.tar.bz2

wget http://downloads.haskell.org/~ghc/8.0.1-rc4/ghc-8.0.0.20160421-x86_64-deb8-linux.tar.xz    

tar xvfj ghc-8.0.0.20160421-x86_64-deb8-linux.tar.bz2
cd ghc-7.10.3  

# install to  
mkdir $HOME/Software/ghc-7.10.3  

./configure --prefix=$HOME/Software/ghc-7.10.3  
make install

# cleanup: remove temporary files  
cd $HOME/Downloads  
rm -rfv ghc-8.0.0*
~~~

## Activation Script

~~~
switchghc 7.10.3 
